{"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "格特魯德真的不再動彈，只剩嘴唇還在蠕動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒你們。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "別格勒讀懂了格特魯德的唇語。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒你死於陰暗的溝渠。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒黑鍵永遠無法擺脫血脈中的瘋狂。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒夕照區走向衰頹。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒萊塔尼亞永遠在巫王的陰影下顫抖。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我詛咒巫王永遠得不到死後的安寧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......實在太難看了。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我承認自己剛剛有些衝動，但緊急處理威脅大眾安全的因素，這也是我的職責之一。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會替你寫一份詳實的報告的，斯特羅洛伯爵。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚安，祝你做個不用詛咒別人的夢。", "name": "別格勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_486_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g8_concerthall_outside_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的手在流血！難道是被源石結晶刺到了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，好像......是出了點血。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你得立刻接受必要的救治——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救治？現在要救治的是白堊啊！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，他......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說那個詞，芙蓉，我求求你......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他......畢竟是感染者，黑鍵，就當是為他考慮，如果你不想聯繫感染者臨終事務處，至少找個密封性良好的房間......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白，我明白......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就......音樂廳休息室吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我送他過去。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，來，我抱你進去。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵小心翼翼地抱起白堊，身上被源石刺出更多傷口，但他無暇顧及。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他抱著朋友慢慢失去溫度的身體，就像抱著一個短暫而美好的夢。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g9_auditorium", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，我們馬上就到了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快的，很快我們就到了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "白堊？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還——活著？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這就帶你出去，去找芙蓉——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把我安頓在這座建築裡吧。", "name": "白堊？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你以後還能回到夕照區，你就會想起，你有一個很好很好的朋友，你和他在這裡爭吵過，歡笑過......", "name": "白堊？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，你和他共同獻上了一場精彩的合奏。", "name": "白堊？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$2"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，你不是白堊，你是——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這難道不是你想要的嗎？", "name": "白堊？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老頭，閉嘴，我不允許你這樣玷污他。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊為了清除塵世之音付出了生命，可塵世之音......還在我的腦子裡？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我警告你，如果你還想模仿他，我不介意在這把自己的頭打爆。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘆息聲）", "name": "腦海中的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我愚蠢的血脈啊。", "name": "腦海中的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再沒有什麼聲音出現在黑鍵耳畔。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是抱著白堊越來越沉重的身體，一步一步地朝夕照廳的休息室走去。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g11_lounge", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去做密封工作，你在沙發上躺好。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的沙發挺軟的，你躺著一定很舒服——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙發、軟......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你甚至沒睡過家裡的......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我大概真是感染了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前要花點精力才能用的法術，現在幾乎不費勁。看來感染了也挺好的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，這樣就差不多了。門等我出去再封上。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......什麼願望嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紀念......對了，紀念。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那把大提琴，我就拿走了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我給你買的東西，現在我又要拿走，真是......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵的嘴唇動了動，沒說出話。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他靜靜站立片刻，彎下腰，輕輕把自己用慣了的長笛放在白堊身邊。"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你之前說想要一個鑽了孔的硬幣，可我現在只剩這把長笛了......", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起。", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起......", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}